{"tid":2122581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新華社：關閉美國駐成都總領館只針對華府少數極端勢力，不針對美國人民","createTime":"2020-07-24T05:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T07:09:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":69,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"8740ef0ed50954c5ec6c75ffee1acfac9e7467b6","tid":2122581,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"社評說，美方蠻橫要求中方閉館之舉，嚴重違反中美領事條約有關規定，是美方對中方單方面發起的又一次政治挑釁，認為美方聲稱關閉中國駐休斯敦總領館的理由，是完全站不住腳。<br />\n  <br />\n社評又指，中國一貫高度重視中美關係，今次被迫採取反制措施，是對美方無理行徑的正當和必要反應，符合國際法及外交慣例，強調此舉只針對美國政府少數極端勢力，不針對美國人民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539633-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539633-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6HwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ae08d22e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539633-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=78697115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539633-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6f614b42cd938426f644ab7349fe1e711697577a","tid":2122581,"uid":207846,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e29f98c3c34339fea585a2dfe8364766dfc601c","tid":2122581,"uid":53003,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"美國人要感恩嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36fc66599dc0ce843e3507b307573e45a6b03e0","tid":2122581,"uid":61180,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T05:27:15.000Z","msg":"學蓬佩奧搞分化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"